  <brief_title>Tigecycline for Treatment of Rapidly Growing Mycobacteria</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use of Tigecycline for Treatment of Serious Infection Due to Rapidly Growing Mycobacteria (Especially M.Abscessus)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
