  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine the safety, tolerance, and efficacy of Tigecycline when given daily to patients
      with rapidly growing mycobacterial disease (especially M.abscessus).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To assess the safety and efficacy of tigecycline in the treatment of drug resistant rapidly
      growing mycobacterial disease especially M. abscessus
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
